Description: 
        
        Run the Tests
        -------------
            
        Install tox and run it::
        
            pip install tox
            tox
        
        Limit the tests to a specific python version::
        
            tox -e py27
        
        Conventions
        -----------
        
        Onegov Newsletter follows PEP8 as close as possible. To test for it run::
        
            tox -e pep8
        
        Onegov Newsletter uses `Semantic Versioning <http://semver.org/>`_
        
